// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4821 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7d9d2404-22f1-58de-9375-493499dfdf90

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
